Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:06.01,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious! As expected from Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:10.65,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's filet mignon de porc à l’Avesnoise, because there was pork left in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:15.12,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,The sauce is surprisingly appetizing. What did you use to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:19.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's made of Madeira wine. The meat was marinated in wine vinegar and beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:21.38,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'll get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:23.16,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.96,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time to eat it, and then have a good sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.37,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:33.84,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Does it remind you... of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It doesn't remind me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:40.26,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,But good things happened as well. For example, Suzaku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:43.05,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was the only time that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:46.97,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The rest was just full of sorrow, and horrible things but.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.56,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Only that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:52.65,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that person hasn't come here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:56.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that he's busy with work at the army. Eventually, Suzaku will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.97,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm referring to C.C..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:01.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:07.28,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's true that you can't date with me around... That's why outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:11.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, you're mistaken. That person isn't anything like a girlfriend... That...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:12.45,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:14.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That... erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:18.58,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, think! I can't say that she's my accomplice... Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:21.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Just plain friends with a woman who comes visiting in the dead of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:22.58,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's not persuasive enough! {Settokuryoku}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:23.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A teacher from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Promising to share my future with a teacher is... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Nunnally doesn't know what C.C. looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.04,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Can I just say that she's a boy whose voice hasn't broken yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.78,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... Even so... Even so... Even so... Even so... Even so... Even so... Even so... {Count number of Sore tomo and adjust while timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:36.23,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,I've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:37.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Sayoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:38.75,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:42.64,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I had to take leave for my own reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:45.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sayoko-san, you were hired by the Ashford family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped that you have to attend to the tasks of the Ashford family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:50.04,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,How was Milly-san's matchmaking session?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.34,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, this is the thirty-first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:57.51,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's as usual. Milly-sama wrecked it herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.70,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's why it ended early?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The president is the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:06.30,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because she already has someone in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.25,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.16,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She just wants to enjoy freedom a bit more, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:10.90,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:14.71,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how she looks, Milly-sama is surprisingly shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:18.80,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,That's very persuasive since Sayoko-san, the housekeeper, is the one saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.34,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nunnally-sama. This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:23.75,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:26.17,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the second issue of the thousand cranes series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:31.68,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there are other good luck charms in Japan that help to grant one's wishes, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.23,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nunnally-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:38.32,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Since you wanted something powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:43.83,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,It feels unusual for a doll... Is it made of a plant...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:50.25,Default,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a doll made of straw. It comes as a set with these five-inch nails. Please use them together.
